-- Barcelona Striker David Villa Breaks Leg In Club World Cup Semifinal
-- B y   T a r i q   P a n j a
-- 2011-12-15T11:52:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-15/barcelona-striker-david-villa-breaks-leg-in-club-world-cup-semifinal.html
Barcelona striker  David Villa 
fractured the tibia in his left leg, the Spanish soccer champion
said on its website today.  Villa got the injury during the first half of Barcelona’s
Club World Cup semifinal match against Qatar’s Al Sadd.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
